00:21:58,124 --> 00:21:59,249
This is Tokyo.

266
00:21:59,332 --> 00:22:02,373
We received this intel
from a North Korean asylum seeker!

267
00:22:05,291 --> 00:22:08,124
All units! Return to base at once!

268
00:22:08,332 --> 00:22:10,332
- Halt op and return at once!
- Nobody move!

269
00:22:28,666 --> 00:22:31,749
We took 8 of your heads!

270
00:22:31,874 --> 00:22:34,249
Stop by any time!

271
