We can't rely on unverified intel.

275
00:22:55,291 --> 00:22:57,416
We will expose the truth today.

276
00:23:05,916 --> 00:23:07,541
They're on the move.

277
00:23:07,999 --> 00:23:10,249
Find the green briefcase, which one is it?

278
00:23:10,332 --> 00:23:12,748
The gray suit is carrying a green briefcase.

279
00:23:14,082 --> 00:23:15,373
Isn't that Director Pyo?

280
00:23:15,457 --> 00:23:16,623
You're right.

281
00:23:16,707 --> 00:23:19,248
He's a key player in the
nuclear development effort.

282
00:23:19,332 --> 00:23:20,832
Everyone on your toes.

283
00:23:20,916 --> 00:23:23,541
This op has to succeed.

284
00:23:25,416 --> 00:23:26,874
One moment.

285
00:23:30,124 --> 00:23:31,332
I'm changing the plan.

286
00:23:31,416 --> 00:23:33,749
Agent Yang get the family,
