291
00:23:43,249 --> 00:23:44,040
The prize comes first.

292
00:23:44,166 --> 00:23:45,332
Initiate!

293
00:23:46,666 --> 00:23:48,707
Says who, dammit!

294
00:23:55,041 --> 00:23:56,541
Agent Yang, what are you doing?!

295
00:23:56,624 --> 00:23:57,707
Listen up!

296
00:23:57,707 --> 00:23:59,873
We are sticking with the HQ's plan!

297
00:24:00,249 --> 00:24:00,999
Stick to the original plan!

298
00:24:00,999 --> 00:24:01,999
Everyone, move!

299
00:24:05,249 --> 00:24:07,290
Turn the car around!

300
00:24:07,749 --> 00:24:08,707
Agent Yang!

301
00:24:08,957 --> 00:24:12,540
The Director said intel on
Donglim is our top priority.

302
00:24:12,749 --> 00:24:14,124
Agent Yang!

303
00:24:17,457 --> 00:24:18,707
Listen up everyone.

304
00:24:18,791 --> 00:24:22,124
When we complete this mission,
everyone will get promoted!

305
00:24:22,207 --> 00:24:23,832
Trust me on this.

306
00:24:41,791 --> 00:24:43,499
Where are you going?

307
00:24:43,707 --> 00:24:46,498
Tae young Corp. in Hakone.

308
00:25:01,999 --> 00:25:03,332
Get in!

309
00:25:08,666 --> 00:25:10,291
- What are you doing?!
- I'm leading this op.

310
00:25:10,374 --> 00:25:13,290
Intel first, what do you know about Donglim?

311
00:25:13,374 --> 00:25:15,957
I said I'll tell you
once we arrive in South Korea.

312
00:25:16,041 --> 00:25:19,249
Spec Ops 417 was wiped out yesterday.

313
00:25:19,582 --> 00:25:21,582
Intel on the mole first.

314
00:25:21,666 --> 00:25:24,291
Is this the best South Korea can do?

315
00:25:24,582 --> 00:25:25,623
Open the door now!

316
00:25:25,707 --> 00:25:29,290
If you don't tell me,
we'll pull out immediately.

317
00:25:30,332 --> 00:25:32,957
Why isn't he letting him in?

318
00:25:33,332 --> 00:25:35,498
On October 15, 1982, Osaka,

319
00:25:35,582 --> 00:25:37,748
and May 11, 1983, Tokyo,

320
00:25:37,832 --> 00:25:41,957
he met North Korea 35 Chief Li Yong-su.

321
00:25:42,457 --> 00:25:45,165
Cross reference it with
flight logs of your agents.

322
00:25:45,249 --> 00:25:47,290
We learned all your top secrets through him,

323
00:25:47,374 --> 00:25:48,790
he's Donglim.

324
00:25:48,999 --> 00:25:50,374
Open the door!

325
00:25:50,457 --> 00:25:51,873
Comrade Pyo!

326
00:25:58,499 --> 00:25:59,957
Comrade Pyo!

327
00:26:00,249 --> 00:26:01,540
Stop!

328
00:26:02,124 --> 00:26:03,665
Open fire!

329
00:26:38,041 --> 00:26:38,999
Chief!

330
00:26:39,082 --> 00:26:41,707
The prize and Agent Yang are trapped at the scene!

331
00:26:41,916 --> 00:26:44,166
Agent Yang is shot and stuck in his vehicle!

332
00:26:44,249 --> 00:26:46,165
What should we do?

333
