Wait, what are you doing?!

334
00:26:55,249 --> 00:26:57,374
Get out! Out!

335
00:26:58,499 --> 00:26:59,749
Please don't do this!

336
00:26:59,832 --> 00:27:00,998
- Where's my husband?
- I'm sorry.

337
00:27:01,082 --> 00:27:03,540
Please don't abandon us!

338
00:27:03,624 --> 00:27:05,082
Listen to me!

339
00:27:22,624 --> 00:27:25,665
Tell them our location! Hurry!

340
00:27:35,666 --> 00:27:36,999
Watch out!

341
00:28:38,207 --> 00:28:39,873
Come out, quick!

342
00:28:42,124 --> 00:28:43,957
Agent Yang first!

343
00:29:00,124 --> 00:29:01,374
Agent Yang!

344
00:29:01,457 --> 00:29:03,040
Wake up, sir!

345
00:29:03,791 --> 00:29:04,832
Agent Yang! Sir!

346
00:29:04,916 --> 00:29:06,207
Sir! Agent Yang!

347
00:29:23,041 --> 00:29:25,332
Are you really not hurt?

348
00:29:25,791 --> 00:29:28,957
Director was summoned and got his ass whipped.

349
00:29:29,249 --> 00:29:31,790
Things are tense because of the botched Pyo op.

350
00:29:31,874 --> 00:29:36,374
Also, the president's Japanese
summit is confirmed, top secret.

351
00:29:39,582 --> 00:29:41,040
Chief.

352
00:29:42,541 --> 00:29:47,041
The intel about Donglim
