353
00:29:55,207 --> 00:29:59,290
How can you botch
every op the president approves?

354
00:29:59,374 --> 00:30:02,832
Fuck, what am I doing with these amateurs?

355
00:30:04,041 --> 00:30:06,166
Resign now, you morons!

356
00:30:07,291 --> 00:30:08,749
Get the fuck out!

357
00:30:15,624 --> 00:30:17,082
What do you want?

358
00:30:17,291 --> 00:30:19,541
Spec Ops 417

359
00:30:19,707 --> 00:30:22,707
was massacred due to your bad judgment.

360
00:30:22,874 --> 00:30:24,082
What the fuck?

361
